{"tid":595659,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[粵語拼音] 西里爾拼音字 Пе̂нкјӓмп","createTime":"2018-03-17T01:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T05:50:01.000Z","uid":8543,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f945e43af997b75f58a496e6bb1e241c979cf00","tid":595659,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:14:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>簡介：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 本方案基於粵語拼音字（Penkyampji）。<br />\n<br />\n2. 本方案採用西里爾字母（Cyrillic Alphabet）。<br />\n<br />\n3. 本方案適合「能編碼西里爾字母」的電腦。<br />\n<br />\n4. 關於Penkyampji的其他特點可參考此網址。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一、字母表</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Аа Бб Гг Дд Ее Жж Зз Ии Йй Јј Кк Лл Мм<br />\n</span><br />\nНн Оо Пп Сс Тт Уу Ўў Фф Хх Цц Ъъ Ыы Ээ<br />\n<br />\n對應：(Aa Bb Gg Dd Ee Jj Zz Ii Yy Yy Kk Ll Mm<br />\n<br />\nNn Oo Pp Ss Tt Uu Ww Ff Hh Cc Qq Eu/eu Eo/eo)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>二、輔音表</strong><br />\n<br />\nб波  п婆  м摸  ф科   д多   т拖   н挪  л羅<br />\n<br />\nг哥   к卡   х何  гу瓜  ку誇  ж左  з左  ц初<br />\n<br />\nс梳   ј也   ў華  нг我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>三、元音表</strong><br />\n<br />\nа    а呀  аи挨  ау拗   ам監    ан晏    анг橫  аб鴨  ад押  аг客<br />\n<br />\nӑ         ай矮  аў歐  амп庵   ант恩  анк鶯  ап急   ат不  ак德<br />\n<br />\nе    е借           еу掉  ем舐                   енг鏡  еб夾             ег尺<br />\n<br />\nӗ         ей非                                       енк英<br />\n<br />\nи    и衣           иу妖  им淹     ин煙               иб葉 ид熱<br />\n<br />\nо    о哥 ои哀                         он安      онг康          од渴  ог惡<br />\n<br />\nо̆        ой去   оў奧              онт春   онк沖           от律  ок屋<br />\n<br />\nэ   э靴                                                  энг香                     эг約<br />\n<br />\nу   у烏   уи會                         ун碗                        уд活<br />\n<br />\nы  ы於                                  ын冤                       ыд月<br />\n<br />\nм  м唔<br />\n<br />\nнг  нг五<br />\n<br />\n藍字 = 短元音，不會實際採用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>四、標調</strong><br />\n<br />\n第一調陰平(55) 陰入(5) 周調：ӓ ё ӥ ӧ ӱ ӭ ӹ  詩/式<br />\n<br />\n第二調陰上(35) 口口(0) 口調：а̃ е̃ и̃ о̃ у̃ э̃ ы̃  史<br />\n<br />\n第三調陰去(33) 中入(3) 店調：а̂ е̂ и̂ о̂ у̂ э̂ ы̂  試/錫<br />\n<br />\n第四調陽平(21) 口口(0) 河調：а е и о у э ы  時<br />\n<br />\n第五調陽上(13) 口口(0) 母調：а́ е́ и́ о́ у́ э́ ы́  市<br />\n<br />\n第六調陽去(22) 陽入(2) 渡調：а̀ ѐ ѝ о̀ у̀ э̀ ы̀  是/食<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.cantonese.asia/thread-33017-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.cantonese.asia%2Fthread-33017-1-1.html&d=tYjTBKIYFpdAGqpvrOmEiDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=76a57405\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.cantonese.asia/thread-33017-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"5d1a7758e53e96dad8b76eaedd4230fb8ab11672","tid":595659,"uid":40216,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T02:36:16.000Z","msg":"比較偏愛拉丁字母，但西里爾字母可以為東斯拉夫地區轉寫粵語"},{"pid":"0978a1a5b37c10347016f2886025a892984596e2","tid":595659,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"474b7bce3fe401c015468bb05e43f184dfb4e62a","tid":595659,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f21e01f54a9a7fe2bc5ccd419f15316cfc69d38","tid":595659,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"有冇例文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f457fc6316ac20441de55ce8275842d3d0a08f4","tid":595659,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8405e008dd8cc1744d5370698bbf1420ddee1a","tid":595659,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"羅馬拼音都搞唔掂仲用西里爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji